    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Excessive use or misuse of drugs, causing physical, emotional, mental, or sensory injury or impairment. For addiction to narcotics or other drugs, use "drug addiction."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000014151/Thesaurus of ERIC Descriptors (1982)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Uso excesivo o mal uso de drogas, causando daño o deterioro físico, emocional, mental o sensorial. Para la adicción a narcóticos u otras drogas, use "drogadicción”.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Overmatig gebruik of misbruik van drugs dat tot fysieke, emotionele, mentale of zintuigelijke beschadiging of verzwakking leidt. Gebruik 'drugsverslaving' voor de verslaving aan verdovende middelen of andere soorten drugs.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099099/Van Dale groot woordenboek (1994)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>意指過度使用或是濫用藥物，因而引起生理、情感、精神或感官上的傷害或損傷。沉迷於使用麻醉劑或其他藥物，則稱為「藥物成癮」。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
